Titolo: A Farewell to Dragons

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: A Farewell to Dragons is a role-playing video game by Russian studio Arise first released on February 19, 2010 for Microsoft Windows. The game is an adaptation of a Russian language fantasy novel by Sergey Lukyanenko and Nick Perumov titled "Не время для драконов" (translated as "Not the Time for Dragons").